{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/sekiro-shadows-die-twice-dark-souls-tenchu/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice Adalah Dark Souls dan Tenchu Dalam Satu Game","content":"<p>Apa yang terjadi jika game fantasi super sulit Dark Souls dan game aksi <em>ninja</em> Tenchu digabung menjadi satu game? Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice-lah jawabannya! Game buatan FromSoftware ini menjadi salah satu sorotan di <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siapa-yang-memenangkan-e3-2018/\">E3 2018</a> lalu. Konsep, <em>gameplay</em>, dan tantangannya mampu mencuri perhatian para <em>gamer</em>. Seperti apa sih keunggulan game ini?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48990\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48990\" data-attachment-id=\"48990\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sekiro-shadows-die-twice-dark-souls-tenchu/attachment/01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48990\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" alt=\"sekiro: shadows die twice\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48990\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: FromSoftware</p></div>\n<p>Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice bercerita tentang seorang <em>shinobi</em> yang tuannya diculik oleh <em>samurai</em> dari klan Ashina. Ketika tuannya diculik, sang <em>shinobi</em> dibunuh dan tangan kirinya dipotong. Akan tetapi ia tidak mati dan terbangun di sebuah tempat misterius yang ditinggali seorang pria tua. Selain itu, tangan kiri sang <em>shinobi</em> pun telah digantikan oleh lengan prostetik berkekuatan magis. Pria tua itu kemudian memanggil sang <em>shinobi</em> sebagai Sekiro, alias Serigala Berlengan Satu. Dengan kekuatan barunya, Sekiro pun memburu sang <em>samurai</em> Ashina untuk menyelamatkamn tuannya dan membalas dendam.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48991\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48991\" data-attachment-id=\"48991\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sekiro-shadows-die-twice-dark-souls-tenchu/attachment/02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48991\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: FromSoftware\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48991\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: FromSoftware</p></div>\n<p>Seperti yang sudah disinggung sebelumnya, <em>gameplay</em> dari Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice menggabungkan elemen <em>action RPG </em>ala Bloodborne dan Dark Souls dengan konsep <em>stealth</em> khas <em>ninja</em> yang jadi ciri khas Tenchu. Sang produser Hidetaka Miyazaki pun mengaku bahwa Sekiro terinspirasi oleh Tenchu, bahkan niatnya Sekiro akan dijadikan sekuel dari Tenchu. Kalimat “Shadows Die Twice” bukan sekedar judul game saja karena jika Sekiro mati, ia bisa hidup kembali walaupun dengan beberapa catatan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48992\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48992\" data-attachment-id=\"48992\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sekiro-shadows-die-twice-dark-souls-tenchu/attachment/03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48992\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: FromSoftware\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48992\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: FromSoftware</p></div>\n<p>Apa yang membuat game ini menjadi lebih unik lagi adalah <em>gimmick</em> tangan mekanik Sekiro yang dapat berubah dan digunakan untuk berbagai macam keperluan. Salah satu fungsinya adalah bisa dijadikan perisai, <em>grappling hook</em>, hingga kapak.  Menurut FromSoftware, Sekiro nantinya akan mendapatkan berbagai kemampuan baru untuk lengannya seiring berjalannya cerita.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48993\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48993\" data-attachment-id=\"48993\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sekiro-shadows-die-twice-dark-souls-tenchu/attachment/04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48993\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: FromSoftware\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48993\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: FromSoftware</p></div>\n<p>FromSoftware nampaknya tidak main-main dalam meramu tantangan dan kesulitan dalam game Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice. FromSoftware mengklaim Dark Souls dan Bloodborne “tidak ada apa-apanya” dibandingkan dengan game ini. Sekiro memang bisa dihidupkan berkali-kali setelah mati, namun hal itu nampaknya hanya menjadi sebuah fitur praktis bagi mereka yang mudah frustasi dengan sulitnya musuh-musuh dalam game ini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48994\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48994\" data-attachment-id=\"48994\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sekiro-shadows-die-twice-dark-souls-tenchu/attachment/05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48994\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: FromSoftware\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48994\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: FromSoftware</p></div>\n<p>Setidaknya <em>gamer</em> nggak akan terlalu bete memainkan Sekiro karena pergerakan karakter dalam game ini nampaknya tidak bakal sekaku Dark Souls dan Bloodborne. Sekiro bisa berkerak sangat luwes dan ia pun mampu bertarung dengan kecepatan yang cukup tinggi. Tentu saja karena Sekiro awalnya adalah seorang shinobi, alias ninja.</p>\n<p>Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice rencananya akan rilis di awal tahun 2019 untuk konsol PS4, Xbox One, dan PC. Mari kita nantikan bagaimana FromSoftware “menghidupkan kembali” game Tenchu yang juga pernah mereka tangani di masa lalu ini. Akankah Sekiro menjadi Dark Souls-nya game <em>stealth ninja</em>?</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4OgoTZXPACo\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"856992f4-7298-543a-a402-79c173452553"}}}